description:
This is a 14 minute workout called 'Meditation for Anxiety - Yoga With Adriene' from the channel Yoga With Adriene.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: 15 Minute Meditation For Anxiety guides you through a simple at home meditation to provide relief from anxiety, stress, and energetic imbalance. Find a comfortable seat, tune into your breath, and soften. Return to this practice regularly for preventative care. Great for beginners!
